$ Visual Studio Code API

*VS Code API* ais a → development/languages/JavaScript API that can be used in → development/editors/Visual-Studio-Code/extensions[VS Code extensions].

{ Language ID

  A language ID can be used, for example, in the `onLanguage` → development/editors/Visual-Studio-Code/extensions/anatomy/package_json#vscode-package-json-activationEvents[activation event].

code {
vscode.TextDocument.getLanguageId()
code }

}

